{
  "stem": "13690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at 10, 11 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So when I noticed the patrol going in from one bar to the other bars-- there were bars for the Germans--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- when they walked in, I crossed the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I crossed--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To run over-- quite difficult, but I run over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I knocked at my father's house where he lived, he was afraid to open the gate of the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was living-- he had a room, one room, in a ground floor level.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said look, I will open the window, you will jump through the window, I said, father, I cannot jump.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hurt myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said I will not be able to jump into the window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he put out a chair, and under the chair I stepped, and then we took the chair back into the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That how I get back into the hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That still was the part of the hundreds, so to say, 70-- starting to come up again and again-- and they left, again, 30 Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That tried to expel my mother with the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we said we're not going to go to Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They want to put us again to Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother said adamantly, the way she heard what's going on then, and I was there, I witnessed myself, seeing that there's practically no room where to go, where to sleep, that she would not let us go.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then she found a Gentile man during the day, and she said, would you take my two children-- my sister, myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eli, I don't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he said, yes, gladly, I will take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You pay me, I will take the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
